    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The House watches the Prime Minister and the other Members of the Government and says whether it has or has not confidence in their general integrity and purpose, and then those Ministers and the Prime Minister watch the others to make sure that they keep up to the mark.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
